channel.title: Game Over - INDIR3CT (Trap)
channel.description:
Hey everyone! So I'm working on a Trap track, and I'm hoping to submit it to a record label such as Hybrid Trap Official, Drop central, Kaliedo collective, or Lowly palace. I got in contact with each one, and I got the information on how to submit my demo.
I have the track I wanted to submit somewhat done, But I need feedback! I uploaded it as a private soundcloud link because of the .wav sample in it.
Please take a listen and let me know where I can improve or what I can do to change!
Thanks so much!!!!!
https://soundcloud.com/indir3ct/gameover/s-G8KrV
